| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0170 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1059b8b2-79fa-5366-a1db-d0d5980904a8"
